                        <additions>
                          <list>
                          <item xml:id="a1">
                            <desc type="Unclear">F. 1v–2v: mälkəʾ-hymn consisting of rhymed stanzas. Incipit: ትጼውረከ፡ ክንፈ፡ ደመና። ምስለ፡ ነፍስየ፡ መአምፅ፡ ቅድመ፡ ትትፋተህ፡ ሲዩና። እስመ፡ አንተ፡ ረዳዒሁ፡ ወአንተ፡ ምእመና።. The text is written in a fine handwriting, characters are broadly spaced. The text is not rubricated, with lacunas in correspondence of the word sälam at the beginning of each stanza.</desc>
                            <locus from="1v" to="2v">Fols 1v–2v</locus>
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id="a2">
                            <desc type="PoemSalam">Salām for St. Mercury <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2888RepCh169">Sälam läzǝkrä sǝmǝkä gäbrä Iyäsus</ref></desc>
                            <locus from="56v" to="60r">Fols 56v–60r</locus>
                            <q xml:lang="gez">ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ ለማርያም፡ በውስተ፡ ውሣጤ፡ መንጦላእት፡ ወይብልዋ፡ በሀኪ፡ ማርያም፡ ሐዳስዩ፡ ጠእዋ፡ ይቤ(50v)ላ፡ መልአክ፡ ለማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ተወከፊዮ፡ ለቃል።</q>
                            
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id="e1">
                            <desc>Pen trials.</desc>
                            <locus target="#60v">Fol. 60v</locus>
                          </item>

                          </list>
                        </additions>

